<p>White Supremacy is defined as the beliefs and ideas purporting natural superiority of the lighter-skinned, or “white,” human races over other racial groups. Today, the term “white supremacist” is used for groups that support extreme nationalism, racism, or hate. These groups often use violence to get what they want.</p>
